[{'id': 1, 'text': 'At first I thought he jammed it by inserting his finger into the trigger guard behind the finger.'}, {'id': 2, 'text': "The Browns don't know shit when it comes to QB's."}, {'id': 3, 'text': "Mario didn't play as many games"}, {'id': 6, 'text': "Amazing, there was actually a time when Xbox Live didn't exist."}, {'id': 9, 'text': 'Synical ploy for SF, there must be an election coming up!'}, {'id': 11, 'text': "if you're not even lvl 30 on your main account no you are not ready"}, {'id': 12, 'text': "because galaxy collapse is a fkin hilarious meme and if you disagree you're obvs wrong"}, {'id': 13, 'text': 'That title belongs to Joe Warren.'}, {'id': 14, 'text': 'There will be 1 more overlap between port and essenjection next week too'}, {'id': 16, 'text': "It's a fake according to Aston Martin!"}, {'id': 18, 'text': 'Can confirm they were at the scrimmage.'}, {'id': 19, 'text': 'Would be an exceedingly easy website to make responsive as well, no real complexities in the design.'}, {'id': 21, 'text': 'I hope she owns that pharmacy in a year or two.'}, {'id': 22, 'text': '0/10 missed the widow mine at the end'}, {'id': 23, 'text': 'What, do you want them NOT to work?'}, {'id': 24, 'text': 'Even though its never revealed he is Gay, he is definitely gay for being a male hairdresser right?'}, {'id': 25, 'text': 'Thank god this oil will keep flowing for months, allowing them ample time to update said technologies.'}, {'id': 26, 'text': 'Way to focus on the issues, gentleman.'}, {'id': 27, 'text': 'The only solution is for citizens to give up their only defense and trust the government will keep us safe.'}, {'id': 28, 'text': 'LOL Thanks Rito for that sweet animation that gives me 7 minutes of joy rather than a new champion that would give me 10,000 minutes.'}, {'id': 30, 'text': 'As a Norwegian, I am livid with their absolute humiliation of my people with this blatant example of cultural appropriation.'}, {'id': 31, 'text': 'Came to look at the comments, was not disappointed'}, {'id': 32, 'text': 'a masked group pelted police with stones and shot fireworks at them, the semi-official Anatolia news agency reported What exactly is a 10 year old doing amongst these people?'}, {'id': 33, 'text': 'If you account for inflation it would be worth 23 USD in 2007.'}, {'id': 35, 'text': "Shouldn't you use PS4/XB1 for this?"}, {'id': 37, 'text': 'I much prefer seeing pictures that belong on Facebook here instead of really interesting pictures like these.'}, {'id': 38, 'text': "it's in the rusted metal tin on the shelf @1:11"}, {'id': 39, 'text': 'What a bunch of big guys, beating up a defenseless girl huddled on the ground.'}, {'id': 43, 'text': 'As long as the breakfast included bacon it should be considered acceptable.'}, {'id': 44, 'text': 'Well he showed he can score on Saturday, so I guess it makes sense'}, {'id': 45, 'text': 'Can we acknowledge that this was a joke and this was just a silly thing I noticed?'}, {'id': 46, 'text': 'But I am so sick of watching Harden he just flops and shoots FTs'}, {'id': 47, 'text': "At least the cop didn't flip out and call in a SWAT team."}, {'id': 48, 'text': "If it's actually putting any pressure on your hard drive right there, that's a great way to destroy the hdd."}, {'id': 49, 'text': "Never has a woman become wet when she didn't want to, or for someone she didn't want to"}, {'id': 50, 'text': 'If you take 200 grand from pharmaceutical companies then probably yes.'}, {'id': 51, 'text': "The just can't help it, he does that cool looking intro dance."}, {'id': 52, 'text': "This will confuse a couple people thinking it's a new Mario Party though"}, {'id': 53, 'text': 'God forbid if the NBA wants their owners to conduct their business with some ethical guidelines'}, {'id': 54, 'text': 'Yes, should give it a good shot in the arm.'}, {'id': 55, 'text': 'In normal things by you, I\'d say "original" as sarcasm, but I have to accpet... this game will be the best in the whole saga, from the looks of it atleast.'}, {'id': 56, 'text': "This just in, Saudi Arabia isn't really an ally and trusting them is leading us down the road of ruin in the ME."}, {'id': 63, 'text': 'Hey, wait a sec... Who cares about this data retention bs, he was speeding!'}, {'id': 64, 'text': "A lot of the lower end donations are still higher than what I'll make in a year."}, {'id': 66, 'text': 'The Firebombing will continue until morale improves and Light the Fuse takes its rightful place at the top of the meta.'}, {'id': 67, 'text': 'Lol, my state can do some crazy shit sometimes.'}, {'id': 69, 'text': 'welp thats enough of this trash'}, {'id': 70, 'text': "Aren't you late for your cross burning, Adolf?"}, {'id': 72, 'text': "His summoner name is C9 KingKiller and it's Plat 1"}, {'id': 73, 'text': 'No candidates lose their right to vote.'}, {'id': 75, 'text': "He didn't come out so much as he was outed by a dumb news reporter"}, {'id': 76, 'text': 'wait nevermind i know what this is'}, {'id': 77, 'text': "On the backside, most small business sales have a non compete clause so that someone doesn't create a successful startup, sale it, and then create a competitor knowing everything there is to know about the business they just sold which is now their rival."}, {'id': 78, 'text': 'Clevs looks like he really wants to be there.'}, {'id': 79, 'text': 'The American economy must be in a really good state if they can just waste 1 billion dollars worth of anything.'}, {'id': 80, 'text': 'B-but if you remove the cervix, your intestines will fall out!'}, {'id': 81, 'text': 'Gotta find that resultant velocity using physics.'}, {'id': 82, 'text': "They should also remove Towers of Doom because I don't like the map."}, {'id': 83, 'text': 'There are no misplays at tournaments, only "interesting lines"'}, {'id': 84, 'text': "And look and that fully automatic Glock assault rifle he's using!"}, {'id': 86, 'text': "Or are we scouting a left winger who happens to be Dejan's brother?"}, {'id': 87, 'text': 'Someone put too much detergent in the washing machine again!'}, {'id': 88, 'text': 'I do totally care about pax'}, {'id': 89, 'text': 'But if the state is owned by the public(or polis), and you are a part of the public, then you own the state, but if you own the state and the state owns you then how can liberty, money, freedom, markets, capitalism, trade?'}, {'id': 90, 'text': "Miyamizu is Mitsuha's surname (last name)"}, {'id': 91, 'text': "If they don't want to use NP links, should we not?"}, {'id': 92, 'text': 'Who better than to communicate with Trump on an equal level.'}, {'id': 93, 'text': 'But she has "come-hither" eyes-she should be stoned to death!'}, {'id': 94, 'text': "I'm sick and tired of people stealing discs and not calling numbers!"}, {'id': 95, 'text': "Probably because of that strong showing by Kaine in the debate that convinced everyone he'd make a great President if anything happens to her."}, {'id': 97, 'text': 'Yo does anyone know when they gonna get released?'}, {'id': 98, 'text': 'dont feed the troll guys downvote and walk away'}, {'id': 99, 'text': 'Bummer for what was otherwise a relatively healthy team'}, {'id': 100, 'text': 'Jeez this paper needs an editor.'}, {'id': 101, 'text': "Yeah game is hard, dont check your debuff, look away, die... That's next level difficulty for sure"}, {'id': 102, 'text': 'But, but, the fraudsters are so good they never get caught!'}, {'id': 103, 'text': '...aaaahnnddd that, folks, is how it works.'}, {'id': 106, 'text': "Don't these silly workers realize that if they demand bathroom breaks, their jobs are just going to be automated more to make up for the additional cost?"}, {'id': 107, 'text': 'I really wish my mum would stop complaining when I call her that.'}, {'id': 108, 'text': 'Some states have actually criminalized ladies nights on the grounds that they are unconstitutional (which technically they are) but what evs.'}, {'id': 110, 'text': "I could have sworn that beef's apron was a slice of pizza I love how Vech's is chasing a bat; that is SOO him"}, {'id': 111, 'text': 'SetEnvIfNoCase User-Agent ^$ bad_bot SetEnvIfNoCase User-Agent "^Curl" bad_bot SetEnvIfNoCase User-Agent "^Wget" bad_bot SetEnvIfNoCase User-Agent "^libwww-perl" bad_bot Yeah, absolutely no problems will arise from blocking these.'}, {'id': 112, 'text': "I thought trolls weren't allowed in this sub how'd you get through"}, {'id': 113, 'text': "Cab Assaults, Hit and Runs, Robberies/Muggings etc..In the past week and a half that's a lot of crime news for Ottawa."}, {'id': 114, 'text': 'i reported this to the mods because of the confederate flag.'}, {'id': 115, 'text': 'I enjoy physically harming people I like!'}, {'id': 117, 'text': 'And also one of the most disappointing'}, {'id': 120, 'text': "This was photoshopped I'm not believing"}, {'id': 121, 'text': 'this should be the one cabinet post where trump actually knows a qualified person and yet... here we are'}, {'id': 122, 'text': 'Those fucking terrorists with their FTP and private mail servers'}, {'id': 125, 'text': 'Another day in Bronze V eh?'}, {'id': 126, 'text': "Someone's got a case of the scribbles."}, {'id': 127, 'text': "Well at least they'll have no problem finding another restaurant job with Paula Deen as a reference"}, {'id': 128, 'text': 'possibly OpTic edition headset or something.'}, {'id': 129, 'text': "I kinda hope the Patriots do win it all so they can drop this tired victim complex they've got going on."}, {'id': 131, 'text': 'As an Eagles fan I am quite against Saban going to the Giants'}, {'id': 132, 'text': 'I hope Slash\'s contract said "No fat Axl"'}, {'id': 135, 'text': 'Quit the game and get a life'}, {'id': 136, 'text': 'OP go get that cat spayed.'}, {'id': 137, 'text': 'Anyone got this without the caption?'}, {'id': 138, 'text': "I'm pretty sure you DO have to have something wrong with you mentally if you think being 600lbs is fine"}, {'id': 139, 'text': 'Yeah I hate all those bandwagon Browns fans we have to deal with.'}, {'id': 140, 'text': '5% on C rotation sure seems reasonable'}, {'id': 142, 'text': 'Who needs clean water when you can pay more per gallon of the bottled stuff.'}, {'id': 143, 'text': 'Well this should fix all their problems.'}, {'id': 144, 'text': 'Thanks for the paywall on Ranked mode!'}, {'id': 146, 'text': "I wonder if this means that the DVR viewership will be down for this episode, since in the first half that's where the ratings saw a large increase."}, {'id': 148, 'text': 'I know all her moves and she knows mine, that means I have the advantage'}, {'id': 149, 'text': "Overpowered as fuck but maybe that's what Priest needs."}, {'id': 151, 'text': 'But Chads are hoarding all the females'}, {'id': 153, 'text': "Comparing against two players doesn't really show a lot especially when you change the players your comparing against."}, {'id': 155, 'text': 'what is cheaper now, toilet paper or rubles ?'}, {'id': 156, 'text': 'Congrats and welcome to the team!'}, {'id': 157, 'text': 'States Rights not "city rights" States always know best, especially when it\'s Alabama.'}, {'id': 159, 'text': 'So is this how they are trying to be more advertiser friendly?'}, {'id': 160, 'text': 'Its nice to hear you talk some sense for a change.'}, {'id': 161, 'text': 'I was hoping this was that video where the guy carries the lady out and uses her head to push the door open.'}, {'id': 163, 'text': 'Fuck you, John, you never did any of that shit and you complained just like we did.'}, {'id': 166, 'text': 'Why does southern Morocco have its own flag?'}, {'id': 167, 'text': 'Wouldnt want someone innocent to catch the gay.'}, {'id': 168, 'text': 'Nice of him to take his snout out of the trough long enough to squeal for the cameras.'}, {'id': 169, 'text': 'King vegeta did almost kill broly'}, {'id': 172, 'text': "ITT: People freaking out over the price tag.. Yeah, because it's not like these will drop in price ever"}, {'id': 173, 'text': 'But but but there is no such thing as kill stealing'}, {'id': 174, 'text': "But that would put guys in the 'friend zone'."}, {'id': 176, 'text': 'user reports: 1: False and/or grossly misleading bullshit Language fail.'}, {'id': 177, 'text': "I'm so sick of the fucking media twisting everyone's words!"}, {'id': 180, 'text': 'Ha ha ha good one, Charlie.'}, {'id': 181, 'text': 'I believe it was made on the RAGE engine.'}, {'id': 182, 'text': 'Now call Comcast and tell them my internet is slow.'}, {'id': 183, 'text': 'Is that a shot at Save us from the Archon style song names as well?'}, {'id': 184, 'text': "I personally wish he'd show some more pizazz in his celebrations, but I know that's not his style."}, {'id': 186, 'text': 'please tell me that its just'}, {'id': 188, 'text': 'How does one even going about becoming an elector?'}, {'id': 191, 'text': "But please, let's keep talking about how she didn't endorse Bernie and how she doesn't deserve any respect."}, {'id': 192, 'text': 'idk maybe (theo,chasun,woosa) and (orion,ritesh,perna) for GWD and (Vanessa,Orion,Perna,Ritesh) for AD'}, {'id': 195, 'text': "Are you complaining that you didn't get ECTO GREEN Greatest Hits?"}, {'id': 197, 'text': 'For every person being queued against a deck that counters them, another person is queued against a deck they counter.'}, {'id': 198, 'text': "man, I kinda wish I updated to windows 10 now... Here's hoping for a windows 8.1 version to come out XD"}, {'id': 201, 'text': 'I guess Luke is the new franchise MLB?'}, {'id': 202, 'text': 'Gotta be about the Weekly Newsletter.'}, {'id': 204, 'text': 'Maybe they should stop doing illegal shit.'}, {'id': 205, 'text': 'Stolen nudes are totally a reason for more security.'}, {'id': 206, 'text': 'They might change their mind if it becomes nothing but conquerors in the top tiers'}, {'id': 207, 'text': 'dont you just hate it hen somebody has to explain every single thing going on in a story?'}, {'id': 208, 'text': 'In other news, water is wet.'}, {'id': 212, 'text': 'Sounds too much like the Chainsmokers in my opinion'}, {'id': 214, 'text': "It's no surprise that the media is all over this damning piece of evidence."}, {'id': 215, 'text': "Parth said Weldon took on the other half of the coaching responsibilities so I feel like the reward was deserved under the pretense that it's actually for the duo (Parth + Weldon)."}, {'id': 216, 'text': 'This is why I love the east coast, we never have to deal with digging our chairs out.'}, {'id': 217, 'text': 'Pedantic and preachy, XKCD at its best.'}, {'id': 218, 'text': "But if it's flat, wouldn't it only be 2D?"}, {'id': 219, 'text': 'He actually shot it on target'}, {'id': 222, 'text': "You get all the fame and glamour of being a reality tv star, isn't that enough?"}, {'id': 227, 'text': 'With that level of airbrushing, this looks more like a Swank circa 1995.'}, {'id': 229, 'text': 'Duty Finder saw all the icons on your UI and thought you were a full party :P'}, {'id': 232, 'text': 'You need at least 4 of these to equal 1 ps4'}, {'id': 234, 'text': 'Good title and in the right sub'}, {'id': 235, 'text': 'HEY HEY hey hey hey hey......I resemble that remark.'}, {'id': 236, 'text': 'i was subbed since 25k the vids have gone to shit'}, {'id': 237, 'text': "I'd buy it if the camo came with about 100mm of extra armor as well."}, {'id': 239, 'text': 'If they were simply honest and told us they set it up this way to increase loot box sales I doubt so many people would be upset.'}, {'id': 240, 'text': "Guess you shouldn't have shot him"}, {'id': 244, 'text': "Don't worry, I'm sure those brave corruption fighters at Wikileaks will expose them!"}, {'id': 246, 'text': 'Hnnnngggggggg I love living in BC'}, {'id': 248, 'text': 'I think if he gets elected again, he needs to just come out with it.'}, {'id': 249, 'text': 'That was me, I got high and started drawing on shit.'}, {'id': 251, 'text': 'Yeah the brm not purifier or po6'}, {'id': 252, 'text': 'Because being loud and throwing insults is how you win an argument.'}, {'id': 255, 'text': 'The war on terror is a huge success~!'}, {'id': 256, 'text': 'The release of Ice Age: Collison Course.'}, {'id': 257, 'text': 'Or play csgo and waste all their money on skins!'}, {'id': 260, 'text': 'The upcoming elections will be conspiracy mud-slinging.'}, {'id': 262, 'text': 'Oh wow I had no idea!'}, {'id': 264, 'text': 'But I thought he was a bust?'}, {'id': 266, 'text': 'Happen to have a link to his watch?'}, {'id': 268, 'text': "How do we know the horse wasn't drunk and actually gave consent."}, {'id': 269, 'text': 'How about making the person(s) who made the accusations pay the costs?'}, {'id': 271, 'text': 'Sure she first called the storm with her witch powers and then bought adds on the weather channel.'}, {'id': 272, 'text': "Most modern games aren't played in a browser."}, {'id': 273, 'text': "I'm sure Mexico will pay for that one too."}, {'id': 274, 'text': 'You would only consider his record outstanding if you were a raci.... oh Spicers statement makes sense now.'}, {'id': 275, 'text': 'He is the monk from the suicide mountain'}, {'id': 276, 'text': "If you've given up already don't bother posting here and wasting our time."}, {'id': 278, 'text': 'He took a sarcastic compliment as a real compliment "Ohh you must read a lot of books"'}, {'id': 279, 'text': 'Because the one thing we were missing this year was offensive fire power, not defensive depth at all'}, {'id': 281, 'text': 'Until they want to fight gay marriage or EPA regulations.'}, {'id': 283, 'text': "But it's more fun to hate on others while remaining anonymous."}, {'id': 287, 'text': 'wow those poor invaders their families should sue the shit out of the little fucker!'}, {'id': 288, 'text': "How 'bout **you** take my upvote and go to hell"}, {'id': 289, 'text': 'What did savage say about injuries?'}, {'id': 297, 'text': 'If your wife originates from your penis, I think we might have a problem or two here.'}, {'id': 298, 'text': "But if he leaves he won't have Tallahassee pd covering for him anymore"}, {'id': 301, 'text': 'This article is almost a year old.'}, {'id': 302, 'text': 'Aah yes, I always knew it was Soros and the NWO.'}, {'id': 303, 'text': "No, it's always been about which console gives you a more consistent 60 fps."}, {'id': 304, 'text': 'I guess they really want Thunder vs Heat'}, {'id': 305, 'text': "I'm sure there are fans in every program that go to far, it's not limited to Baylor."}, {'id': 306, 'text': 'That guy is so far up himself'}, {'id': 310, 'text': 'Is that your girlfriend in that picture :O'}, {'id': 311, 'text': "I'm not a corporate shill or a fake account, just like 99.9% of reddit seems to be"}, {'id': 315, 'text': 'The one that empowers women and supports more women and black people in movies.'}, {'id': 319, 'text': 'How can we possibly make this hellhole more intolerable...?'}, {'id': 322, 'text': 'How the fuck did that get so rusty?'}, {'id': 323, 'text': 'Good for me,I will study physics or math on college,so maybe secure job if I am good enough.'}, {'id': 324, 'text': 'I knew we were a disease.'}, {'id': 326, 'text': 'wow thats sad af fucking retarsd op'}, {'id': 327, 'text': "That's it thats the show My god... Way too many spoilers here"}, {'id': 329, 'text': "I mean, if all you're going to do is write clickbait it does the job nicely."}, {'id': 334, 'text': 'How do you clip music to your shirt?'}, {'id': 336, 'text': '2016 might be a little late for that.'}, {'id': 337, 'text': 'The norman bates comment was a very nice touch.'}, {'id': 338, 'text': 'Old white man with fragile masculinity talks about how women are ruining everything.'}, {'id': 339, 'text': 'Salamie generally, but specific classes would want Behemoth with specific skill boosts.'}, {'id': 341, 'text': "And don't place your self worth in your social media likes/followers/etc."}, {'id': 343, 'text': 'Now you can XYZ summon 1 stars I guess'}, {'id': 344, 'text': 'This just in, CEO of Gamergate calls Manned Mars Mission Vaporware!'}, {'id': 345, 'text': 'Take the ceiling off of taxable income and means test for benefits.'}, {'id': 346, 'text': 'I agree what was he thinking?'}, {'id': 347, 'text': "SHE SHOULDN'T BE ALLOWED TO DO THAT BECAUSE..."}, {'id': 348, 'text': 'Real rap, Tupac never died he just put in new contacts'}, {'id': 349, 'text': 'You can tell the pc is vr ready because it has a vga output at the front.'}, {'id': 350, 'text': 'Alternate Headline: Rich guy finds out that having to work for a living is hard.'}, {'id': 351, 'text': "I mean I've been wanting some mastery skins, so I'm kinda happy."}, {'id': 353, 'text': 'If cats came from lions then why are there lions?'}, {'id': 355, 'text': "and they don't know what happened in Afganistan on any particular day either"}, {'id': 356, 'text': 'Ricciardo is already getting the psychological advantage for next season'}, {'id': 357, 'text': 'I hear a cold front is gathering near Monolith.'}, {'id': 358, 'text': 'Luckily they were all wearing gloves.'}, {'id': 359, 'text': "Don't worry, just get some tongs and drain the sink!"}, {'id': 361, 'text': "Guys if we tell them who's in the database, they'll go and change their biometrics!"}, {'id': 364, 'text': 'Ah, French men, glad to see some of them have not forgotten to be creepy'}, {'id': 366, 'text': 'Is this the largest prize pool tourney to be won by a stand-in?'}, {'id': 367, 'text': 'Because we need less infrastructure and more condos downtown'}, {'id': 369, 'text': 'Sorry, The President was drunk last night'}, {'id': 370, 'text': "Right, and since I'm now pissed off, I *must* be PMSing."}, {'id': 371, 'text': 'Basically "I wish protestors would be quiet and well-behaved so I could continuing ignoring their plight"'}, {'id': 373, 'text': 'The owner of that car will be SO happy to get his car back!'}, {'id': 374, 'text': 'Just raise it to 100 and barely anyone will smoke!'}, {'id': 375, 'text': 'So this guy managed to pull his phone and gun out just in time for this idiot to pull up beside him, all while steady driving.. Talk about multitasking.'}, {'id': 376, 'text': "hehehehe they didn't spell police right hehehehehehehe"}, {'id': 377, 'text': 'friendly reminder that I currently hold the high score at ~12,000 cuck points step it up cb2'}, {'id': 378, 'text': 'I think everyone knows it was taxing the mines that brought about the recession.'}, {'id': 379, 'text': "Kyle Seager was as good if not better than Machado last year but he isn't even as respected as his rookie younger brother"}, {'id': 382, 'text': 'God, what a bunch of tender-hearted pansies you Brits are.'}, {'id': 383, 'text': 'But that was wolf, not Game and Watch.'}, {'id': 385, 'text': 'Fun fact: Nobody ever killed each other before Trump was elected'}, {'id': 389, 'text': 'Maybe Nash needs a night to recover from getting tackled and molested last night'}, {'id': 390, 'text': "Focusing on the important issues....I'm sure this will cut down terrorism"}, {'id': 391, 'text': 'Do we have to resign this every 7 days as well?'}, {'id': 392, 'text': 'Haha, yes lets make jokes about causing brain damage in babies.'}, {'id': 394, 'text': '633 net upvotes even though this bill has fuck-all to do with mass surveillance.'}, {'id': 395, 'text': 'This is just more proof of labors waste with that fancy ftth thingy, thankfully the adults are back!'}, {'id': 396, 'text': 'Hilarious whining about how much the far right hates being forced to treat other humans with simple respect.'}, {'id': 398, 'text': 'Wait, I thought Trump said there was no drought.'}, {'id': 399, 'text': "I'd rather continue pirating my material, thankyouverymuch."}]
