[{'id': 400, 'text': 'Hey man, the size should be 300x100 , your aspect ratio is way off the chart.'}, {'id': 401, 'text': "As long as they weren't seen as being racist for pointing out that one oriental guy amongst all those middle eastern and african people, then that is all that matters"}, {'id': 403, 'text': "That's the first thing I thought when I saw this picture!"}, {'id': 405, 'text': 'Big Sean would decimate King Kenny.'}, {'id': 408, 'text': 'PC gamer are so fucking terrible nowadays with shit posting articles'}, {'id': 409, 'text': 'i thought only Jews have rights to use it'}, {'id': 410, 'text': 'Lucky his daughter had her helmet on.'}, {'id': 411, 'text': 'Come on people, everyone knows snowmen are created by humans so the world and the universe must be created too.'}, {'id': 412, 'text': 'Just mix your meats like the rest of us, ya damn purist'}, {'id': 415, 'text': "Dammit BB, I told you we should've put them in the storage area!"}, {'id': 416, 'text': 'I vote Klingon as the 2nd language!'}, {'id': 417, 'text': 'No, why would you say that?'}, {'id': 418, 'text': "Don't make me put my foot down."}, {'id': 419, 'text': 'and the upscaled 4K which is indistinguishable from native 4K'}, {'id': 422, 'text': "I'm just glad he didn't start by rising his spork."}, {'id': 423, 'text': "It's good to know that the NSA is doing such a good job of being a National Security Agency."}, {'id': 425, 'text': "im offended you're offended, now what?"}, {'id': 427, 'text': 'Wow I wonder how all these sprouts survived without the novice network.'}, {'id': 428, 'text': 'Person here: This is called a nail.'}, {'id': 429, 'text': "Wow, what an awful typo OP LOL it's clearly Orariguid Flethic"}, {'id': 430, 'text': "Oh, forgot to mention, I'm currently testing out stuff"}, {'id': 431, 'text': 'Lol mental illness is hilarious you guys...'}, {'id': 432, 'text': 'Step 1: He was in over his head in the NFL.'}, {'id': 438, 'text': "I'm sure Arsenal are shitting themselves at the thought of it."}, {'id': 439, 'text': 'What if the photographer is a woman?'}, {'id': 440, 'text': 'But I pay to play the game how I want!'}, {'id': 441, 'text': 'Shocking that an Abrahamic religion has been in America since George Washington'}, {'id': 442, 'text': 'So basically Gurley is a lil bitch'}, {'id': 443, 'text': 'WELL NOW THIS IS THE LAST STRAW!'}, {'id': 446, 'text': "I don't blame them, people are not giving it negative reviews over a single bad thing that has happened, they are giving it multiple negative reviews do to the past 2-3 years of promises yet no real substance unless you count the paid duck update because that totally rocked"}, {'id': 448, 'text': 'I\'ve literally heard his, "white people have contributed the most to society," argument in a KKK documentary.'}, {'id': 450, 'text': 'oh gosh those "truthers" are the worst'}, {'id': 451, 'text': 'I wish we were still in the days where we take guys like this out back and beat them with hoses.'}, {'id': 452, 'text': "How is it these legislators don't leave them selves open for law suits?"}, {'id': 453, 'text': 'You sure we should still be using that racist meme?'}, {'id': 454, 'text': 'Geeze you guys are just as bad as the birther movement, does he need to release his birth certificate too?'}, {'id': 456, 'text': "Amongst people I know personally, it's more like 1 in 50."}, {'id': 457, 'text': 'General Assembly is really earning their salary.'}, {'id': 458, 'text': 'Excellent for all those males who sexually harass me in Apoc.'}, {'id': 459, 'text': "The real question is: who's the babe (m'lady) in the picture?"}, {'id': 460, 'text': 'Yeah, 6 wins 1 draw and 1 loss is such a poor way to qualify.'}, {'id': 462, 'text': 'What if this is really about Cespedes and the Jay Bruce thing is just a fake out?'}, {'id': 463, 'text': 'dude, you need to contain those unbidden'}, {'id': 464, 'text': 'The best of luck to our striking Finnish cousins.'}]
